title: AFC West Prospect Matchmaker (Russell Wilson update coming later today) (Football 4/16)
description:
UPDATE: Russell Wilson inked a record deal after this podcast was published. Stay tuned for analysis of that contract coming up later Tuesday on the Pick Six podcast. 
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest Russell Wilson news, take a look at the best matches for each team in the AFC West in terms of prospects and then analyze the season premiere of Game of Thrones.
